{"tid":1170660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本千葉縣南部發生5.1級地震","createTime":"2019-05-25T06:56:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T12:11:01.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"33a546d688280e9bd4d030b5423bc2dd682a8bf0","tid":1170660,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T06:56:45.000Z","msg":"日本千葉縣南部周六（25日）下午發生黎克特制5.1級地震，東京地區均有震感。暫時沒有海嘯威脅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2837862/org/f6cb61e715e6fb1aa03fd5ce985038a1.jpg/4aqEUC6FDkZK2crYEJWdkXD9mvjNJBBunenAEZ3pwBE?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2837862%2Forg%2Ff6cb61e715e6fb1aa03fd5ce985038a1.jpg%2F4aqEUC6FDkZK2crYEJWdkXD9mvjNJBBunenAEZ3pwBE%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=4c652816&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本地震：千葉縣5.1級地震，東京地區震感明顯。（日本放送協會截圖）<br />\n<br />\n地震在當地下午3時20分發生，震源深度為40公里，震央位於千葉縣南部。<br />\n<br />\n千葉縣長南町的震度最高，達到5弱級。東京都中央區的震度為4級。其他地方如茨城縣、神奈川縣、埼玉縣、群馬縣等均錄得震感。<br />\n<br />\n氣象廳表示，目前沒有海嘯威脅。<br />\n<br />\n日本放送協會報道，這是千葉縣自2018年7月以來發生的最大震級地震。2018年7月7日，千葉縣東部外海出現6級地震。"},{"pid":"b3822f6cc3590d4470aaef3632c59e65988dba33","tid":1170660,"uid":33439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T06:57:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"025bb8d842f47ac467e3329d15264eec9a2510ea","tid":1170660,"uid":198035,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T06:58:19.000Z","msg":"朱閪教授<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c8af0ffdc806356d01c08af532c47eae79d3ad2","tid":1170660,"uid":235152,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T07:24:59.000Z","msg":"成個亞洲狂震,睇來好快有8級以上超強地震"},{"pid":"79c62abce9c9c79e308a2a5ec1c0892ce7a0848c","tid":1170660,"uid":42340,"like":2,"dislike":18,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T07:26:52.000Z","msg":"抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d895bded2e0ad92e674cf5518f10bf87c036b15e","tid":1170660,"uid":18666,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T07:39:13.000Z","msg":"住咗喺日本大半年 呢啲地震一兩個禮拜就有一次 唔使預言都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d3bbff8a547c0d16091134268624e4462c7e88","tid":1170660,"uid":196099,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"d895bded2e0ad92e674cf5518f10bf87c036b15e","tid":1170660,"uid":18666,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T07:39:13.000Z","msg":"住咗喺日本大半年 呢啲地震一兩個禮拜就有一次 唔使預言都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T09:34:24.000Z","msg":"你住係沖繩？咪撚on9<br />\n最大震度5弱呀 強い地震嚟架<br />\n係氣象廳要開記者會<br />\n総理官邸危機管理中心要設立情報聯絡室嘅level 嚟<br />\n之不過日本基建好 呢個程度嘅震度唔足以釀成大規模災害啫<br />\n<br />\n根據日本氣象廳嘅分類<br />\n震度1から3まで 地震<br />\n震度 ４ やや強い地震（稍強地震）<br />\n5から7まで 強い地震 （強烈地震）<br />\n<br />\n2017年全國47個都道縣府只有7次震度5弱以上嘅地震<br />\n2018年為11次<br />\n而氣象廳同各放送局喺首都圈以外都係以5弱為判定強震嘅基準而發表緊急地震速報"},{"pid":"470b130115e69f759daa0fa4e54ca145ff97641c","tid":1170660,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T09:37:13.000Z","msg":"原來5級<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afac3c3876a03d598bb72c06d1947d888526944d","tid":1170660,"uid":12455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T09:58:51.000Z","msg":"最近都諗緊東京呢排冇震過咁滯<br />\n點知一震就咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4a7227dbd1e3ce4709a7847b4179476ec3225b2","tid":1170660,"uid":84275,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c0d3bbff8a547c0d16091134268624e4462c7e88","tid":1170660,"uid":196099,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"d895bded2e0ad92e674cf5518f10bf87c036b15e","tid":1170660,"uid":18666,"like":11,"dislike